# mails.com workspace

For task execution workflow, read [`agent-workflow.mdc`](agent-workflow.mdc).

This folder is a **docs-only meta-repo**. Code lives in two separate GitHub repos — never commit child folders here.

| Folder | Repo | Port (local) | Deploy |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| `mails-backend/` | `mails-com/back` | `:3000` | Fly.io `mails-back.fly.dev` |
| `mails-frontend/` | `mails-com/front` | `:3001` | Cloudflare Workers `front.aitor.workers.dev` |

## Read before editing

- **Backend:** [`mails-backend/README.md`](mails-backend/README.md) + [`mails-backend/.cursor/rules/project-stack.mdc`](mails-backend/.cursor/rules/project-stack.mdc)
- **Frontend:** [`mails-frontend/README.md`](mails-frontend/README.md) + [`mails-frontend/CONTRIBUTING.md`](mails-frontend/CONTRIBUTING.md)

## Run locally

```bash
make dev   # Overmind: backend :3000 + frontend :3001
make stop  # stop both
make sync-contracts  # after editing backend contracts/user.json — sync to frontend
```

Needs Overmind (`brew install overmind`), Postgres, and env files in each child repo. See README for first-time setup.

Login = browser redirect to backend `/auth/google`. API = `fetch` with `credentials: "include"`.

## PR quality gates

- Backend: Lefthook + CI (`sqlc generate` before build)
- Frontend: `npm run validate`
